This module allows to print from POS a ticket without price or taxes

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Usage
=====

POS printing proxy mode must be disabled, then you can generate the ticket
without price through the POS receipt screen.

Known issues / Roadmap
======================

- Implement ticket without price generation on proxy mode.
